Package org.ginsim.core.graph

Interface GraphAssociation<AG extends Graph<AV,​AE>,​AV,​AE extends Edge<AV>>

  • Type Parameters:
    AG - ag graph
    AV - av vertex
    AE - ae edge
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DynamicGraph, HierarchicalTransitionGraph, ReducedGraph<AG,​AV,​AE>, TrapSpaceInclusionDiagram
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDerivedGraph, DynamicGraphImpl, HierarchicalTransitionGraphImpl, ReducedGraphImpl, TransitionGraphImpl, TrapSpaceTreeImpl
    public interface GraphAssociation<AG extends Graph<AV,​AE>,​AV,​AE extends Edge<AV>>
    Defines a graph associated with the implementor of this interface. This interface should be implemented by all objects which depend on a separate Graph for interpretation. This association will ensure that this associated graph can be retrieved properly.
    Author:
    Lionel Spinelli, Aurelien Naldi
